Packages 
Package Description
grid
Grid package A package containing the necessary classes and methods to build a grid with obstacles and tuples with special costs, as well as providing classes to easily identify the position of an individual in the Grid, and calculating the cost of the path it has taken throughout his life
parser
Parser package A package containing the necessary classes and methods to implement the XML parser required by the Simulator simulation
pec
PEC package A package containing the necessary classes to implement a simulator based on a private event container.
population
Population package A package containing the necessary classes and methods to store and implement the evolution of individuals throughout a stochastic simulation as well as a Comparator implementations to sort any kind of List from the JDK library.
simulator
Simulator package A package containing the necessary classes and methods to store, simulate, and show the results of the evolution of individuals through a stochastic simulation, making use of classes and methods from the JDK library, as well as the created population, pec, parser and grid packages.
